high_descs: Turn around the locate the computers on the low table.
Pick up the newspaper from the table.
Take the newspaper and turn right, and then left to the small table in the corner of the room.
Turn on the lamp on the small table.
anns.task_desc: Take the newspaper and turn on the light.

high_descs: Turn around, walk to the coffee table
Grab the newspaper on the coffee table
Turn right, walk to the end, turn left, walk to the side table
anns.task_desc: Grab the newspaper on the coffee table, turn on the lamp on side table

high_descs: Turn to the left and walk straight. Then turn right to go towards the two laptops.
Pick up the newspaper that is sitting in front of the laptops.
Turn right to go towards the switch on the wall. Make a left and go to the white table with the lamp on it.
Turn on the lamp that is on the table.
anns.task_desc: While holding the newspaper turn on the light on the table.
